┤Kathleen Bird 
100 yrs.
So many memories with still more to come
Sit here and enjoy the little things in life
because one day you'll look back and realise
they were the big things."║
ĘJohn Selwyn Geary (1935-2016)
A very special Daddy and Grandad.
Love Jennifer, Amanda and Ian
"Your presence we miss, your memory we treasure
loving you always, forgetting you never.""┐
